(41342, 87813, 0, 7, 'I Will Sing', '編曲: Ray Lin\r\nGuitars and Bass by Ray Lin\r\nDrums by Adam Dunn ', '2011-12-21 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 4, 'F     F/A    Gm7      C7sus\r\nA little baby was born for us all \r\nF      F/A     Gm7  C7sus\r\nand His name is Jesus\r\nF     F/A       Bb        Dm7\r\nEmmanuel God is with us we know\r\n        Gm7      C7sus    F\r\nThrough Christ our Jesus our Lord\r\n     \r\n      F         F/A\r\nLet us sing let us sing\r\n      Bb            F/A\r\nLet us sing with the angels\r\n       Dm7      Gm7   C7sus \r\nWe will sing of His glory forever\r\n      F         F/A\r\nI will sing I will sing\r\n      Bb            F/A\r\nI will sing with the angels\r\n       Dm7      Gm7   C7sus  C7   F    F/A    Gm7  C7sus\r\nI will sing of His mercies fore-------ver  more \r\n\r\nthe King of kings was once slain for us all\r\nHe was there on the cross\r\nBut He rose with the promise of God\r\nHe''d finished what God had begun\r\n\r\nthe Son of God is now seated above\r\nat the right hand of God\r\ninterceding for us whom He loves\r\nand soon will come back to us', '', 250, '', 'Ray Lin', 'Ray Lin', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2011-12-21 11:57:47', '2015-03-12 13:49:38', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
